title: Leading Causes Death ZIP 99-13
description:
Leading Causes of Death by ZIP Code, 1999-2013

Deaths by Cause of Death, by Zip Code 1999-2013 (By Place of Residence): This dataset is for death of California residents, by cause of death, by Zip Code, for year 1999-2013. The death counts per cause of death, represents the deaths to California residents, regardless of the place of death occurrence. A non-California resident who die inside of California would not be included in the dataset.

Source: https://catalog.data.gov/dataset/leading-causes-of-death-by-zip-code-1999-2013
